OL,3,CSmall v Big Prides: How can they
OL,4,Ccompete with the threat of LGBTQ+ hate?
OL,6,FThe organisers of Coventry Pride say
OL,7,Fthey've received hate online including
OL,8,Fa threat to ram a car into the
OL,9,Ffestival crowd.
OL,11,FIt's left them having to spend a huge
OL,12,Fpercentage of their funding towards
OL,13,Fsecurity, and hoping community
OL,14,Fsponsors and fundraisers would help
OL,15,Fwith the cost of putting on the event
OL,16,Fin June.
OL,18,FIt comes as more than 600 LGBTQ+ hate
OL,19,Fcrimes were recorded by West Midlands
OL,20,FPolice in Birmingham alone last year.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
