OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1779541873
OL,3,CSmall v Big Prides: How can they
OL,4,Ccompete with the threat of LGBTQ+ hate?
OL,6,FCoventry Pride is a free event,
OL,7,Fcompared to other larger events like
OL,8,FBirmingham Pride.
OL,10,FIt'll be held at the FarGo Village on
OL,11,F27th and 28th June, which they have
OL,12,Fbeen given for free.
OL,14,FThe chair of the event, Nick
OL,15,FCherryman, told ITV News Central that
OL,16,Fthough he is used to such threats,
OL,17,Fhe's worried about younger people who
OL,18,Fmay be discovering their sexuality and
OL,19,Fmight be deterred from coming to pride
OL,20,Fevents.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1779541873
OL,3,CSmall v Big Prides: How can they
OL,4,Ccompete with the threat of LGBTQ+ hate?
OL,6,FHe said: "We had someone threaten to
OL,7,Fdrive a car into the parade as it
OL,8,Fwere. What I worry about is say, the
OL,9,Fyoung trans person or the young person
OL,10,Fjust coming to terms with their
OL,11,Fsexuality going 'Oh no am I going to
OL,12,Ffeel ok coming here? Am I going to be
OL,13,Fa victim, am I going to be attacked
OL,14,Fand stuff?'
OL,16,F"It does mean a large amount of what
OL,17,Fvery small budget we have will go on
OL,18,Fthings like security. We can't do
OL,19,Fthese events if we can't keep people
OL,20,Fsafe along side making them feel like
OL,21,Fthey belong here."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
