OL,3,CSmall v Big Prides: How can they
OL,4,Ccompete with the threat of LGBTQ+ hate?
OL,6,FCrime and Policing Bill
OL,8,FOn April 29th, the Crime and Policing
OL,9,FBill was given Royal Assent, changing
OL,10,Fthe law to make anti-LGBTQ+ hate crime
OL,11,Fan aggravated offence.
OL,13,FThis change in law brings penalties
OL,14,Ffor anti-LGBTQ+ hate crime in line
OL,15,Fwith offences motivated by race and
OL,16,Freligion, and will give LGBTQ+ victims
OL,17,Fand survivors more time to access
OL,18,Fcriminal justice.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
