OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1779541873
OL,3,CSmall v Big Prides: How can they
OL,4,Ccompete with the threat of LGBTQ+ hate?
OL,6,FNick says: "Whilst it's a step in the
OL,7,Fright direction, there's a long way to
OL,8,Fgo before we can get to a situation
OL,9,Fwhere people are accepted, not
OL,10,Ftolerated."
OL,12,FIn Birmingham alone, 634 LGBTQ+ hate
OL,13,Fcrimes were recorded by West Midlands
OL,14,FPolice last year.
OL,16,FMore than 200 were classed as 'causing
OL,17,Fintentional harassment, alarm or
OL,18,Fdistress'.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
