OL,3,CSmall v Big Prides: How can they
OL,4,Ccompete with the threat of LGBTQ+ hate?
OL,6,FLarger prides, like Birmingham Pride,
OL,7,Fsay they spend a six figure sum on
OL,8,Fsecurity each year.
OL,10,FBut festival Director, Lawrence Barton
OL,11,Fsaid he's ambitious to make the event
OL,12,Ffree in the near future.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1779541873
OL,3,CSmall v Big Prides: How can they
OL,4,Ccompete with the threat of LGBTQ+ hate?
OL,6,FHe said: "The ambition is that Pride
OL,7,Fbecomes a free festival but in order
OL,8,Fto do that, we have to have sufficient
OL,9,Fsponsorship and partners and donators
OL,10,Fbecause all the provisions that Pride
OL,11,Fabsolutely requires, toilets;
OL,12,Fsecurity; fencing; road parking
OL,13,Fsuspensions and the council costs,
OL,14,Fjust to clean the site is #20,000.
OL,16,F"So to find the money to do a free
OL,17,Ffestival on the scale that Birmingham
OL,18,FPride is will be very challenging. But
OL,19,Fit's my ambition.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1779541873
OL,3,CSmall v Big Prides: How can they
OL,4,Ccompete with the threat of LGBTQ+ hate?
OL,6,F"And what we won't do is hold an event
OL,7,Fwhere we don't have sufficient and
OL,8,Fappropriate provisions to keep people
OL,9,Fsafe. It's absolutely critical, it's a
OL,10,Fvital element.
OL,12,F"Is it possible? Yes. Will it be a
OL,13,Fchallenge? Yes."
OL,15,FBirmingham Pride and West Midlands
OL,16,FPolice
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
