OL,3,CSmall v Big Prides: How can they
OL,4,Ccompete with the threat of LGBTQ+ hate?
OL,6,FThis year's Birmingham Pride takes
OL,7,Fplace on the 23rd and 24th May, with
OL,8,Fthe parade due to set off from
OL,9,FVictoria Square and continue towards
OL,10,Fthe LGBTQ+ village in Digbeth on
OL,11,FSaturday.
OL,13,FWest Midlands Police said it would
OL,14,Fhave a police operation in place at
OL,15,FPride and it remained fully supportive
OL,16,Fof its officers from all backgrounds,
OL,17,Fadding it was working to build
OL,18,Fpositive relationships with the public.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1779541873
OL,3,CSmall v Big Prides: How can they
OL,4,Ccompete with the threat of LGBTQ+ hate?
OL,6,FIt said: "We have staff from many
OL,7,Fdifferent backgrounds, including the
OL,8,FLGBTQ+ community and we remain fully
OL,9,Fsupportive of them.
OL,11,F"The acting chief constable has met
OL,12,Fwith representatives of the LGBTQ+
OL,13,Fcommunity and our own force network to
OL,14,Flisten and hear their experiences,
OL,15,Faccounts and views.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1779541873
OL,3,CSmall v Big Prides: How can they
OL,4,Ccompete with the threat of LGBTQ+ hate?
OL,6,F"In the meantime, West Midlands Police
OL,7,Fis committed to policing without fear
OL,8,For favour and continuing to strengthen
OL,9,Fand build positive relationships with
OL,10,Fthe public to ensure they have trust
OL,11,Fand confidence in the force.
OL,13,FLast year, the organisers of
OL,14,FBirmingham Pride banned uniformed
OL,15,Fpolice and senior officials from
OL,16,Fmarching after they claimed then-chief
OL,17,Fconstable Craig Guildford had
OL,18,Frepeatedly refused to apologise for
OL,19,Fhistoric injustices towards the LGBT
OL,20,Fcommunity.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
